[BREAKING]: Leads to outdated commands and tests not working and hence
the inability to launch MainApp, namely AddCommand, EditCommand,
ListCommand, DeleteCommand, and about anything that makes changes to
the model.

Creates new fxml files (BuyerListCard.fxml, SellerListCard.fxml,
DisplayableListPanel.fxml) and modifies existing fxml files to
include new components (MainWindow.fxml).

In essence, any @FXML tag in the JavaFX handlers must match the
components in the corresponding .fxml files, else a Null
Pointer Exception is thrown when either the .fxml file or the
fxml components are missing.
